text: Micah Franklin (born 2 September 1992) is a Bermudian professional squash player. As of February 2018, he was ranked number 223 in the world. ==References== Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Bermudian male squash players Category:Squash players at the 2014 Commonwealth Games Category:Squash players at the 2018 Commonwealth Games Category:Commonwealth Games competitors for Bermuda Category:Squash players at the 2019 Pan American Games
